<GXX>Service management
<WBX>Launch nginx, php-fpm, and keydb:
 <CXX>docker compose up -d
<WBX>Launch angular webpack dev server:
 <CXX>APPS="<YBX><app> <CLR><YXX>[<app> ...]<CXX>" docker compose up --force-recreate angular_dev_server -d

<GXX>One-off tasks
 <CXX>docker compose run --build --rm angular_app_build <YBX><app> <CLR><YXX>[<base-href> [<other-args...>]]
 <CXX>docker compose run --build --rm angular_node_modules
 <CXX>docker compose run --build --rm php-composer

<GXX>Create starter projects
 <CXX>docker compose run --build --rm angular_create_starter <YXX><app>
 <CXX>docker compose run --build --rm laravel_create_starter

<GXX>Tail the logs: <CXX>docker compose logs -f
<GXX>Interactive terminal in container: <CXX>docker compose exec -it -u root <YXX><service><CXX> bash
<GXX>Install inside container: <CXX>apt update; apt install -y iputils-ping telnet vim less
<GXX>Mini reset: <CXX>docker compose down --rmi all --remove-orphans
<GXX>Full reset: <CXX>exit<CLR> <WXX>back to WSL, then <CXX>dcl reset
<GXX>Redisplay this: <RBX>dchelp

